doc:
Returns the last key-value pair in the map.
The key in this pair is the maximum key in the map.

# Examples

```
use std::collections::BTreeMap;

let mut map = BTreeMap::new();
map.insert(1, "b");
map.insert(2, "a");
assert_eq!(map.last_key_value(), Some((&2, &"a")));
```
